title: Merge pull request #66 from makifund/add-video-support
message:
Merge pull request #66 from makifund/add-video-support

Basic video support

title: durationLimit() is in millseconds
message:
durationLimit() is in millseconds

This fixes the camera crash issue when setting the optional
videoLengthLimit attribute. The video camera stops recording once the
limit has been reached.

title: videoLengthLimit improvement
message:
videoLengthLimit improvement

Since VideoRecorderActivity.durationLimit(…) results in the camera
crashing, I’ve adjusted it so that you can’t select a video that is
longer than the optional videoLengthLimit. It’d be nice also if the
in-app camera would also enforce the limit, but this is a good
improvement for now
